description:
Available in English. 

At Atomic-Labs, we know how to appreciate a good cult, and "The Church of the Subgenius" definitely fits the bill. Learn more about the churchly happenings of the Church of the Subgenius by listening to the Weekly Radio Ministry- The Hour of Slack. Learn about upcoming events of Slack. Learn what it means to be pink. This app even includes a link to where you can become an ordained minister and conduct marriage ceremonies.

How do you become a follower of Bob and get started down a path of slack? Well you can start by downloading this app.
